John,

I was with the Pitt Comp Sci Dept when our 1055 system arrived and so I'd
put the time around early '72.  By summer '73 we had added a single KI 
system and we planning to upgrade it to a dual as well.  By Fall '73, I
was working at DEC.

You may also be right about the original KA/KI monitors being able to handle
