assumptions.  Like 0 is *always* the master (system sleep/reconfigure needed
to have the "policy" CPU be elected and float since you could take CPU0
offline for service).  Places were the code wanted to notify "the other" CPU
needed to become "all other active" CPUS.  Stuff like that.
